{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"87c6a33bb8","title":"“苏联出兵匈牙利是是破坏国际法”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6e06168e0b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"87c6a33bb8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0ae4893607","name":"卢冕持"},{"id":"15349243c8","name":"潘相臣"},{"id":"4ad12d831d","name":"杨汝栩"},{"id":"55d4e5b786","name":"中国人民大学"},{"id":"60f90412f6","name":"崔志敏"},{"id":"81f4d5d760","name":"韩枫"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6cb1d9548b","type":"title","text":"“苏联出兵匈牙利是是破坏国际法”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87c6a33bb8"},{"id":"32b5b68c60","type":"authors","text":"中国人民大学崔志敏杨汝栩卢冕持潘相臣韩枫","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87c6a33bb8"},{"id":"b97072af41","type":"paragraph","text":"“苏联第一次出兵匈牙利是破坏国际法，是干涉内政。”（中国人民大学马列主义教研室资料员  崔志敏）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87c6a33bb8"},{"id":"dfaabc6bae","type":"paragraph","text":"在匈牙利事件发生后他说：“苏联出兵是干涉内政，违犯联合国宪章。”（中国人民大学历史系学生  杨汝栩）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87c6a33bb8"},{"id":"db0f375b33","type":"paragraph","text":"“波匈事件发生，苏联要负责任”。在匈牙利事件中“苏联第一次出兵是错误的”。（中国人民大学革命史教研室助教  卢冕持）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87c6a33bb8"},{"id":"6495d2316f","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党一方面空扬反对侵略，但苏联却干涉了匈牙利内政。”（中国人民大学历史系学生  潘相臣）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87c6a33bb8"},{"id":"50fd0bd83f","type":"paragraph","text":"“纳吉基本上是革命的，他的措施是一种策略，因为当时人民反苏、只是为了缓和一下，对人民让步，这样做法，仅是种软弱的表现，不同意说他是反革命分子。”（中国人民大学统计系学生  韩枫）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87c6a33bb8"},{"id":"e4dddaef15","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87c6a33bb8"}],"page":{"id":"3457eb7cea","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"87c6a33bb8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}